HCLT’s infrastructure services lineage and AI strategy position it well to gain market share.
Raise EPS est. by 1% & expect 9% EPS CAGR in FY26-28.
Superior growth/FCF conversion will support premium valuations
Nomura on HCL Tech
Buy, TP Rs 1660
