ICICI Prudential Life Q2 profit up 18% to ₹296 crore The company had logged a net profit of ₹251 crore in July-September 2024-25 By  PTI Updated - October 14, 2025  at 03:47 PM. | New Delhi × Share WhatsApp X Facebook LinkedIn Messenger Reddit Mail https://www.thehindubusinessline.com/money-and-banking/icici-prudential-life-q2-profit-up-18-to-296-crore/article70162141.ece Copy ICICI Prudential Life Insurance Company on Tuesday reported 18 per cent growth in consolidated net profit at ₹296 crore for three months ended September 30, 2025. The company had logged a net profit of ₹251 crore in July-September 2024-25. Its net premium income rose to ₹11,843 crore in the quarter under review from ₹10,754 crore in the year-ago period, ICICI Prudential Life said in a stock exchange filing. Shares of ICICI Prudential Life were trading 0.92 per cent higher at ₹599 apiece on the BSE . Comments Published on  October 14, 2025 READ MORE THIS AD SUPPORTS OUR JOURNALISM. SUBSCRIBE FOR MINIMAL ADS. THIS AD SUPPORTS OUR JOURNALISM. SUBSCRIBE FOR MINIMAL ADS. THIS AD SUPPORTS OUR JOURNALISM. SUBSCRIBE FOR MINIMAL ADS.

