Title   : OYO founder Ritesh Agarwal takes inspiration from Jeff Bezos, says success needs planning: ‘Hope is not a plan’
Source  : www.livemint.com
Published: 2025-10-13T18:25:27
Fetched : 2025-10-14T10:44:04.383170
URL     : https://www.livemint.com/companies/oyo-founder-ritesh-agarwal-takes-inspiration-from-jeff-bezos-says-success-needs-planning-hope-is-not-a-plan-11760378273389.html
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
