Meanwhile, upcoming regulatory changes (CAFE, 2W ABS) & state government tax hikes may erode the GST cut benefits
Prefer premiumization plays M&M, TVS & Hyundai (all Buy), while see downside risk for Hero, Bajaj (both Sell) & Maruti (Neutral)
