Persistent Systems Q2 results live: Q2 profit at ₹471.5 cr
Persistent Systems reported consolidated net profit for the quarter ended September 2025 at ₹471.5 crore as against ₹324.99 crore in the corresponding quarter last year.
- October 14, 2025 15:39
Stock market live: Sensex, Nifty end in red
