- October 14, 2025 15:21
BoM Q2 results live: Key highlights
➢ Total Business grew by 14.20% to ₹ 5,63,909 crore.
➢ Total Deposits increased by 12.13% to ₹ 3,09,791 crore.
➢ Gross Advances increased by 16.83% to ₹ 2,54,118 crore.
➢ Credit - Deposit (CD) Ratio improved to 82.03%.
➢ Gross NPA declined to 1.72% as on 30.09.2025.
➢ Net NPA declined to 0.18% as on 30.09.2025.
➢ Provision Coverage Ratio stood at 98.34%.
➢ Net Profit increased by 23.09% to ₹ 1,633 crore.
➢ Operating profit grew by 16.91% to ₹ 2,574 crore.
➢ Net Interest Income increased by 15.71% to ₹ 3,248 crore.
➢ Net Interest Margin (NIM) stood at 3.85%.
➢ Cost to Income Ratio improved to 37.10%.
➢ Return on Assets (ROA) improved to 1.82%.
➢ Return on Equity (ROE) stood at 22.58%.
➢ CRAR improved to 18.13% of which Tier I is 14.96%.
