Title   : Q2 Results Live Today: BoM, Persistent Systems, ICICI Prudential & IREDA Q2 profit up, Aditya Birla Money profit declines, Tech Mahindra, ICICIGI, Cyient DLM to announce Q2 results
Source  : www.thehindubusinessline.com
